    "body" : "<p>For <strong>Windows</strong> Platform:</p>\n\n<p>try Running the <strong>64 Bit</strong> exe version of IntelliJ from a path similar to following.</p>\n\n<p>note that it is available beside the default idea.exe</p>\n\n<p>\"C:\\Program Files (x86)\\JetBrains\\IntelliJ IDEA 15.0\\bin\\idea<strong>64</strong>.exe\"</p>\n\n<p><a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/a/29897690/184572\">link</a></p>\n"
